1.I efarmogi tha dimiurgi mia sira apo workers diergasies,pou mazi me tin efarmogi tha apantoun se erotimata

./diseaseAggregator -w numWorkers -b bufferSize -i input_dir
numWorkers:O arithmos Worker diergasion pou tha dimiurgei i efarmogi
bufferSize:To megethos tu buffer gia diavasma meso pipes
input_dir:ena directory to opoio periexei subdirectories me ta arxia pou tha epeksergazonte oi Workers.Kathe subdir tha exei to onoma mias xoras kai tha periexei arxeia me onomata pou ine imerominies tis morfis DD-MM-YYYY.Paradeigma:
/input_dir/China/21-12-2019
/input_dir/Italy/01-02-2020

Kathe arxio DD-MM-YYYY periexei eggrafes asthenon kai kathe grammi perigrafi ena astheni pu pire eksitirio/isixthe ekini tin mera.Paradigma:
/input_dir/Germany/02-03-2020
889 ENTER Mary Smith COVID-2019 23
125 EXIT Jon Dupont H1N1 62

Gia kathe eggrafi EXIT tha prepi idi na iparxi sto sistima mia eggrafi ENTER sto idio recordID kai progenesteri imerominia eisagogis.Se diaforetiki periptosi tiponete i leksi ERROR.

TO DO:
1)I efarmogi ksekinontas dimiurga numWorkers Workers child processes kai moirazei omoiomorfa ta subdirs me tis xores pou vriskontai sto input_dir stus Workers
2)Oi Workers tha enimeronontai meso named pipes gia ta subdir pou tha analavoun
3)Otan i efarmogi enimerosi tus workers tha perimeni apo tin isodo entoles apo ton xristi
3)Oi workers tha diavazun ta arxia me xronologiki sira apo tus katalogus pu tus anatethikan kai tha gemizi mia sira apo domes dedomenon pou tha xrisimopioi gia na apantai ta erotimata pu tha stelni o parent
4)Otan o worker teliosi me tin anagnosi enos arxiou,tha stelni meso namedpipe sto parent process summary statistics tou arxiou.Otan teliosi me ola ta arxia enimeroni to parent process oti ine etimo na dexti aitimata
5)An enas Workers labi signal SIGINT i SIGQUIT tha tiponi se arxio log_file.xxx statistika me tis xores kai ta aitimata pu anelave
6)An o worker lavi ena SIGUSR1 sima simeni oti iparxun nea arxia sta subdirs tou opote ta vriski ta diavazi kai enimeroni tis domes tou,kai tha stelni statistics sto parent process(bullet 4)
7)An enas worker termatisi ksafnika to parent process tha prepi na ton antikatastisi
8)To parent process tha prepi na xirizete ta simata SIGCHLD,SIGINT,SIGQUIT
9)An to parent process lavi sima SIGINT i SIGQUIT tha prepi prota na teliosi tin epeksergasia tis trexousas entolis tu xristi kai afu apantisi tha stelni sima SIGKILL stous Workers.Tha tus perimeni na termatisun kai sto telos tha tiponi se ena arxio log_file.xxx to onoma olon ton xoron pou "simmetixan" stin efarmogi me dedomena,ton sinoliko arithmo aitimaton pu dextike apo ton xristi kai apantise me epitixia kai ton sinoliko arithmo aitimaton pou proekipse kapio error

 
